shapes

Class RadialElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • shapes.GraphicElement
      • shapes.RadialElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Circle, RegularPolygon

    public abstract class RadialElement
extends GraphicElement
    Represents a radial object on the canvas. A shape should extend this class if it can be characterized by a center point and a radius.
    See Also:
    GraphicElement, Circle, RegularPolygon, Star
